title: Meteletsa - Winter of the Dead
description:
Russian Winter is a terrible thing... especially if it arrives in mid-July. Out amidst the icy storm, something raises its hideous head - a Russian zombie - senseless and merciless.

Director: Nikolai Pigarev (as Nikolay Pigarev)
Writers: Mikhail Borzenkov, Nikolai Pigarev (as Nikolay Pigarev)
Stars: Mikhail Borzenkov, Tatyana Zhevnova, Aleksandr Abramovich

Taglines: Russkiy zombi - bessmyslennyy i besposhchadnyy. (A Russian zombie is mindless and merciless.)
